  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Multicentric randomized Italian clinical trial, open label, not for profit. To evaluate the
      efficacy of 25-OH-D vitamin in terms of myocardial infarction, stroke, sudden death, death
      for other causes in chronic haemodialysis patients. Two arms of treatment: 25-OH-D vitamin
      per os versus no treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
